            'text_line_9'  => 'LimaTours will use whatever means reasonably available to them to facilitate that the material service providers accept liability and indemnify for and against ',
            'text_line_10' => 'any claims by the CLIENT\'s clients regarding the provision of services intermediated by LimaTours. Therefore, the CLIENT agrees to file any claim/legal action or ',
            'text_line_11' => 'complaint directly with the material service provider and acknowledges that LimaTours does not manage or have any control over the provision of services by the material service provider.',

            'text_line_12' => 'All claims must be filed by the end consumer at the destination. Both the CLIENT and the end client (whether or not this agreement has been terminated) shall at all times hold LimaTours ',
            'text_line_13' => 'harmless and indemnify LimaTours from/against any and all actions, claims, proceedings, losses, costs, expenses and ',
            'text_line_14' => 'lawsuits (including costs and expenses incurred in the defense) arising directly or indirectly from a breach by or on behalf of the CLIENT or the client or any of its employees, agents, representative contractors, associates,',
            'text_line_15' => 'franchisees, etc. with respect to any of the provisions set forth in these General Conditions.',

            'sub_title'    => 'DISCLAIMER OF LIABILITY',
