            'text_line_4' => 'access codes to computer systems, information regarding users, telephone numbers, e-mail addresses, Know-How, formulas, processes, content of the offers submitted',
            'text_line_5' => 'and any other documentation, data or support material of LimaTours to which the CLIENT may have access.',
            'text_line_6' => 'Notwithstanding the provisions of this Clause, it is accepted that the confidentiality obligation shall not apply in the following cases: ',

            'text_line_7' => 'a) When the information is in the public domain or, once the information has been supplied, it enters the public domain, as long as it is not a consequence of non-compliance with this Clause. ',
            'text_line_8' => 'b) Any information that has been disclosed by a third party and is not of a confidential nature, as long as said third party was authorized to disclose that information.',
            'text_line_9' => 'c) When the disclosure is required by law or by judicial or administrative order. ',

            'text_line_10' => 'In the case set forth in paragraph c), the content of such disclosure shall be limited to what is strictly necessary to comply with the legal, administrative or judicial requirement, but does not exempt',
            'text_line_11' => 'from the duty to comply with the confidentiality obligation to disclose the information to other third parties, nor does said information thereby become information in the public domain for the',
            'text_line_12' => 'purposes of the provisions of paragraph a). Likewise, the other party shall be notified in advance of said request, undertaking to make every effort ',
            'text_line_13' => 'to ensure that the information is treated confidentially. ',

            'sub_title_2'  => 'CONFIDENTIALITY',
            'text_line_14' => 'It is expressly forbidden the total or partial disclosure, to third parties, natural or legal persons outside this relationship, of all Confidential Information to which the CLIENT may have access ',
            'text_line_15' => 'through the contracting and execution of their Tourist Services without the express prior authorization of LimaTours.  ',

            'text_line_16' => 'The CLIENT guarantees that its employees, consumers, suppliers, subcontractors and other related persons comply with the confidentiality obligations. It will be their sole',
            'text_line_17' => 'esponsibility to take the necessary measures for this purpose, as well as the claim or damages arising from breach of this obligation. The CLIENT undertakes to maintain these',
            'text_line_18' => 'confidentiality obligations indefinitely, whether or not the relationship between the parties is terminated, from the date of execution of this agreement.',


